# Build output, managed deps, and scratch (added 2026-06-03)
# build_*/ catches any alternate/side-by-side build dir (build_desktop, build_v5_eth, ...)
build_*/
managed_components/
dependencies.lock
scratch/
serial_log.txt
post_issue_comments.ps1

# Code-review fixes session scratch (added 2026-06-08)
build_*.log
.claude/
# Smoke-test tooling: keep the reusable scripts, ignore generated images/logs
.smoke/*
!.smoke/*.py

# Session build/verify iteration scratch logs (added 2026-06-09)
b[0-9]*.log
verify_*.log
host_test*.log

# Root scratch dumps & alternate build dirs (added 2026-06-14, audit #50)
# Serial/boot/SIP-probe dumps land at the repo root as _<name>.txt; flash logs as
# flash_*.log. build-host/ is a side-by-side host build dir that build_*/ misses
# (no underscore). drawbridgepatch/ is a superseded local patch tree.
_*.txt
flash_*.log
build-host/
drawbridgepatch/

# Shareable binary packages (built locally from build_host_ssh; never commit binaries)
dist/

# Hyphenated local build dirs (build-verify, build-host, ...) — the build_*/ glob
# above misses these; without this, a stray `git add -A` swept the whole tree in.
build-*/

# Sensitive business strategy, sales, and vendor-specific files — NEVER commit
BUYER_VALIDATION.md
MONETIZATION_STRATEGY.md
PITCH_SHEET.md
PRICING_MODEL.md
SOAK_TEST_CHECKLIST.md
ntp_verify.txt
reference/
components/3cx-callcontrol-xapi.yaml

# Internal engineering docs (security findings, audit reports, design specs for unbuilt features)
docs/internal/
